<font size="16sp">
"The bomb has been planted". Such  words that bring joy and excitement.  
If you understand what I'm talking about and have friends that feel  
the same way, form up a team and battle like-minded individuals in  
the paradise that is CounterStrike. 
<br>
<br>
<b>Rules and Regulations</b>
<br>
<br>
The teams will be divided into different pools.
<br>
Top two teams from each pool will qualify to the next round. 
<br>
Round robin format with 16 rounds is allowed. 
<br>
Best of 3 formats would make a lead.
<br>
In case of tie, winner is decided based on winning margin.
<br>
<i>5 vs 5</i> game play.
<br>
There should be 32 bit play mode.
<br>
<i>Scroll Duck</i> is strictly prohibited.
<br>
<i>Window mode</i> is not allowed.
<br>
Only 1 substitution is allowed before the match.
<br>
Misconduct will lead to disqualification.
<br>
